(1) A person shall apply to the Council for registration as a social worker in the prescribed manner and form on payment of a prescribed fee.
A person shall apply to the Council for registration as a social worker in the prescribed manner and form on payment of a prescribed fee.
(2) The Council may determine different fees for different classes of social workers.
