(1) There is established a Disciplinary Committee which consists of the following part-time members appointed by the Council : (a) the Chairperson ; (b) the Vice-Chairperson ; (c) four registered association members who are not members of the Council elected at a general meeting of the Association ; and (d) a legal practitioner nominated by the Law Association of Zambia .
